ui]]<br>{{flagicon|USA}} [[Kjell N. Lindgren]]\n| 22 July 2015<br>{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Soyuz TMA-17M]]\n|colspan=2 | [[International Space Station|ISS]] <br>([[Expedition 44|crew 44]]/[[Expedition 45|45]])\n| 11 December 2015<br>{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Soyuz TMA-17M]]\n| align=\"left\"|ISS crew rotation.\n|-\n! rowspan=2|308\n| style=\"padding-left:0.5em\" style=\"padding-left:0.5em\" align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Sergey Alexandrovich Volkov]]\n|rowspan=2 | 2 September 2015<br>{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Soyuz TMA-18M]]\n|colspan=2 | [[International Space Station|ISS]] <br>([[Expedition 45|crew 45]]/[[Expedition 46|46]])\n| 2 March 2016<br>{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Soyuz TMA-18M]]\n| rowspan=2 align=\"left\"|ISS crew rotation.\n|-\n| style=\"padding-left:0.5em\" align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|DEN}} [[Andreas Mogensen]]<br>{{flagicon|KAZ}} [[Aidyn Aimbetov]]\n| colspan=2 | [[International Space Station|ISS]]\n| 12 September 2015<br>{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Soyuz TMA-16M]]\n|-\n! 309\n| style=\"padding-left:0.5em\" style=\"padding-left:0.5em\" align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Yuri Malenchenko]]<br>{{flagicon|USA}} [[Timothy Kopra]]<br>{{flagicon|UK}} [[Tim Peake]]\n| 15 December 2015<br>{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Soyuz TMA-19M]]\n|colspan=2 | [[International Space Station|ISS]] <br>([[Expedition 46|crew 46]]/[[Expedition 47|47]])\n| 18 June 2016<br>{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Soyuz TMA-19M]]\n| align=\"left\"|ISS crew rotation.\n|-\n! 310\n| style=\"padding-left:0.5em\" style=\"padding-left:0.5em\" align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Aleksey Ovchinin]]<br>{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Oleg Skripochka]]<br>{{flagicon|USA}} [[Jeffrey Williams (astronaut)|Jeffrey Williams]]\n| 18 March 2016<br>{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Soyuz TMA-20M]]\n|colspan=2 | [[International Space Station|ISS]] <br>([[Expedition 47|crew 47]]/[[Expedition 48|48]])\n| 7 September 2016<br>{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Soyuz TMA-20M]]\n| align=\"left\"|ISS crew rotation.\n|-\n! 311\n| style=\"padding-left:0.5em\" style=\"padding-left:0.5em\" align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|RUS}} [[An